This module implements minimal Google's ProtoBuf primitives.

Imports

../varint, ../utility, ../utils/sequninit

ProtoField = object
  index*: int
  case kind*: ProtoFieldKind
  of Varint:
    vint*: uint64
  of Fixed64:
    vfloat64*: float64
  of Length:
    vbuffer*: seq[byte]
  of Fixed32:
    vfloat32*: float32
  of StartGroup, EndGroup:
    nil
